ption\": \"Provide clear fix instructions\"}",
      "output": "=== Frappe Setup Fix ===\n\nIssues found:\n1. App created with --no-git flag (missing essential files)\n2. Missing __init__.py, hooks.py, setup.py\n3. Frappe v11 is end-of-life (needs v15+)\n4. 'bench stop' command doesn't exist in v11\n\n=== Solution ===\n\nTo fix your Frappe setup:\n\n1. Stop services (if available):\n   bench restart || echo 'No running services'\n\n2. Remove broken app:\n   rm -rf /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/apps/fg_firstgens_app\n\n3. Create app properly (without --no-git):\n   cd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\n   bench new-app fg_firstgens_app\n\n4. Install app into site:\n   bench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_firstgens_app\n\n5. Start services:\n   bench start\n\n=== Key Fix ===\nUsing '--no-git' prevents proper app initialization.\nRemove --no-git so bench creates all necessary files.\n",
