      "text": "Perfect! Now I can see this is a FirstGens Community platform - the project we were looking for! The README confirms this is:\n\n1. A community platform for first-generation university students\n2. Both a clickable prototype AND a technical blueprint for a production Frappe platform\n3. The project is named \"FirstGens Community — Platform Prototype & Blueprint\"\n\nThis is exactly the project mentioned in the Frappe app we were discussing earlier (with the same branding \"FirstGens\"). The user was saying this project is located in their Documents folder under \"LLM-Test\" in the path `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\community-launchpad-proto`.\n\nSo this is the actual project that needs to be set up as a Frappe app! This is what they want me to help fix.\n\nLet me read more of the README to understand the full project structure and what needs to be fixed.",
