      "text": "You're absolutely right to ask about upgrading all at once! The current Frappe v11 setup needs a comprehensive upgrade. Let me diagnose and fix this systematically.\n\n## 🔍 Current State Analysis:\n\n**What we saw in the logs:**\n- Frappe v11 was used (deprecated, end-of-life)\n- Apps created with `--no-git` (incomplete structure)\n- Missing `bench stop` command (v11 limitation)\n- Security and feature gaps\n\n## ✅ Comprehensive Upgrade Solution:\n\n### 1. **Upgrade Frappe Bench System:**\n```bash\n# Navigate to your Frappe Bench directory\ncd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\n\n# Check current Frappe version\nbench --version\n\n# Upgrade to latest (v15+)\nbench get-app frappe --update\n```\n\n### 2. **Upgrade All Existing Apps:**\n```bash\ncd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\n\n# List all installed apps\nbench list-apps\n\n# Upgrade each app to v15+\nbench get-app <app-name> --update\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app <app-name>\n```\n\n### 3. **Upgrade Specific Apps:**\n\n**For your Frappe apps:**\n```bash\n# Upgrade fg_companion\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_companion\n\n# Upgrade any other apps\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app <app-name>\n```\n\n### 4. **Verify Upgrade:**\n```bash\n# Check Frappe version after upgrade\nbench --version\n\n# List all upgraded apps\nbench list-apps\n```\n\n## 📋 Complete Upgrade Script:\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# Frappe Comprehensive Upgrade Script\n\necho \"🔄 Starting Frappe comprehensive upgrade...\"\necho \"=================================\"\n\ncd /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench\n\n# 1. Backup current setup\necho \"📦 Creating backup...\"\ncp -r /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/apps /home/andiekobbie/frappe-bench/apps_backup_$(date +%Y%m%d)\n\n# 2. Upgrade Frappe itself\necho \"🔄 Upgrading Frappe framework...\"\nbench get-app frappe --update\n\n# 3. Upgrade all apps\necho \"🔄 Upgrading all Frappe apps...\"\nfor app in $(bench list-apps); do\n    echo \"📦 Upgrading $app...\"\n    