      "text": "The user is running commands in the WSL environment, and I can see that:\n\n1. They've already created the `frappe-bench` directory\n2. They've installed git, python3, python3-pip, and nginx using apt\n3. They tried to install frappe-bench via pip but got an error about externally-managed-environment\n\nThis is a common issue with newer versions of Ubuntu (like Ubuntu 24.04) that have PEP 668 (externally-managed-environment) which prevents pip from installing packages system-wide.\n\nThe solution is to use a virtual environment. Let me provide the correct commands they need to run.",
