      "tool": "bash",
      "code": "{\"command\": \"cd ~/frappe-bench\\npython3 -m venv env\\n\\n# Now install frappe-bench in the virtual environment\\nsource env/bin/activate && pip install frappe-bench\\n\\n# Test the installation\\nsource env/bin/activate && bench --version\\n\\n# Create a new bench project\\ncd ~/frappe-bench\\nbench init -v version-15 myproject\\n\\n# Navigate to the project and create your Frappe app\\ncd myproject\\nsource ../env/bin/activate && bench new-app fg_companion\\n\\n# When prompted for your Frappe app, use:\\n# Frappe Version: version-15 (Recommended)\\n# App Title: Fg Companion\\n# App Description: Events, Mentors, AI sentiment & vector search for FirstGens Community\\n# Publisher: FirstGens\\n# Email: admin@firstgens.test\\n\\n# Install the app\\nbench --site firstgens.localhost install-app fg_companion\\n\\n# Start services\\nbench start\", \"description\": \"Execute the complete Frappe Bench setup commands\"}",
